title: Bottle Service Secrets - How to Dominate the Nightlife Scene (Episode 222)
description:
Show Notes:

3:15: Want to know the secret to choosing the perfect table? We spill the beans on how to score the best spot in the club.
5:45: Don't show up to the party too early or too late! Discover the optimal time to arrive for maximum fun with our insider tips.
8:13: Are you ready to take your party to the next level? Learn how to transition from pre-party to bottle service like a pro.
10:05: Bottle service can be expensive, but it doesn't have to be! Discover the economics of bottle service and how to make your money go further.
11:25: Looking for love in all the wrong places? We reveal the best spots to find girls in the club.
12:29: Don't waste your money on the wrong girls! Learn how to spot bottle rats and avoid them like a pro.
16:06: Ready to reach critical mass at the table? We share their secrets to making your party the talk of the club.
17:25: When new girls show up at your table, what's the best way to handle it? We share their tips on how to interact with all your guests.
19:09: Want to take your party to the next level? Discover the game-changing item you need to have at your table.
19:35: Find out the optimal male to female ratio at the table and how to ensure everyone has a good time.
22:05: Feeling down at the club? We share tips on how to improve your mood and make the most of your night.
25:19: What do you do when your guests are being annoying? Discover the best ways to handle difficult situations with our expert advice.
28:06: Love posting on Instagram? We share their thoughts on how much content you should be filming and posting during the night.
29:43: Want to combine bottle service with your social circle game? Discover the winning formula for success with our expert tips.
30:60: What happens at the after party? We reveal their secrets for making the most of the night after the club closes.
30:54: Don't screw up the most tricky part of the evening! We share tips on how to make sure everything goes smoothly.
34:30: Coordinating your group can be tough. Discover the best ways to organize and coordinate exiting the club and arriving at the after party.
37:18: Want to be a valuable addition to your party team? Learn how to make yourself indispensable with our advice.
38:13: Are you the first one to the after party? Discover the important job you need to do to ensure everything runs smoothly.
38:30: When is the best time to mention your table to girls you're trying to recruit? We reveal the optimal moment to bring it up.
40:12: Don't waste your money on unnecessary bottles! Discover the best ways to make your bottles go further and conserve your spend over the night.
41:22: What are the best booze and mixers to order for maximum fun? We share their favorite drinks to order at the club.
42:00: Looking to bring more girls to your table? Learn how to use eye contact and hand gestures to attract them like a pro.
42:30: Want to take a break from the club? Discover the best ways to utilize the smoking patio and still have a great time.
42:55: When's the best time to get her IG? We share tips on when to make your move.
46:21: Don't get hung up on the wrong things! We reveal what to focus on and what to let go of.
48:35: Your vibe can make or break your night. Learn how to put out a positive energy and attract the right people to your table.
49:39: Want to create maximum attraction with multiple girls at the table? Discover how to use competition to your advantage with our expert advice.
51:35: Approaching girls can be intimidating, but it doesn't have to be! We share why approaching with the objective of getting them to your table can be a great exercise.
53:30: Loud music can be a buzzkill, but we have the solution! Discover our tips for dealing with noise and talking to girls.
54:14: Want to recruit girls with a funny routine? We share our favorite comedy routines for bringing girls to your table.
54:55: Looking to position yourself for success at the club? Discover how to talk into girls' ears without being awkward with our expert advice.

To listen to more episodes of the Inner Confidence Podcast, visit the links below:
Website: https://innerconfidence.com/podcast/

And if you're interested in learning more about my coaching services and connecting with me, check out these links:
LinkTree: https://linktr.ee/Robbiekramer
Main Site: https://innerconfidence.com/
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/robbie_kramer/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@robbie.kramer
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/innerconfidence

Thank you for tuning in, and I look forward to helping you build your inner confidence and achieve success!

Join us : https://innerconfidence.com/leverage/
Book a call with me : https://start.innerconfidence.com/video1
